CHROMA ATE INC (2360)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 26.66% to NT$403,148,000 from NT$549,672,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            403,148          549,672    
YOY%             -26.66%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,996,623        3,158,335   
YOY%             -36.78% 
=================================================================
 